Class SPARQL_Upload

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.jena.fuseki.servlets.ActionBase
      • org.apache.jena.fuseki.servlets.ActionService
        • org.apache.jena.fuseki.servlets.SPARQL_Upload
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ActionLifecycle, ActionProcessor
    public class SPARQL_Upload
extends ActionService
    Upload data into a graph within a dataset. This is fuseki:serviceUpload. It is better to use GSP or quads POST with the body being the content. This class works with general HTML form file upload where the name is somewhere in the form and that may be after the data. Consider this service useful for small files and use GSP or quads POST for large ones.
